WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.371 --> 00:00:05.005
Hello.

2
00:00:05.005 --> 00:00:08.541
I'm Jared Bunch, former NFL
player and current high school head coach.

3
00:00:08.541 --> 00:00:11.611
And welcome to the Safe to Compete Parents
Training.

4
00:00:12.245 --> 00:00:15.782
As a parent, you play a critical role
in helping your child participate

5
00:00:15.782 --> 00:00:17.250
in sports safely.

6
00:00:17.250 --> 00:00:20.053
Sexual abuse in youth
sports is preventable.

7
00:00:20.754 --> 00:00:23.523
This training will teach you the skills
you need to keep

8
00:00:23.823 --> 00:00:26.993
the young athletes in your life safe.

9
00:00:27.861 --> 00:00:31.498
In this training, you will learn
to communicate with children and adults

10
00:00:31.498 --> 00:00:35.235
about safe
boundaries and abuse prevention,

11
00:00:36.169 --> 00:00:39.706
to find ways to take action and address
harmful behaviors of others.

12
00:00:40.273 --> 00:00:45.545
And describe how to report concerns
and respond to disclosures.

